Recreating GL Batches from ConnectWise Accounting Interface

This task will retrieve Unposted Invoices, Unposted Expenses and/or Unposted Procurement data from a previously updated Batch within the Accounting Interface in ConnectWise. This task is typically used for integrations with accounting systems, as the data provided from ConnectWise includes the general ledger account number.

Settings

Connection

Required The ConnectWise Company to Recreate the GL Batch data from.

Output File

Required An absolute or relative file path on the local computer or network to save any downloaded data to.

Download Unposted Expenses

Required Specify whether Unposted Expenses should be included in the data. This will be defaulted to False.  

Download Unposted Invoices

Specify whether Unposted Invoices should be included in the data. This will be defaulted to True.  

Download Unposted Procurement

Required Specify whether Unposted Procurement should be included in the data. This will be defaulted to False.

Excluded Expense Record ID’s

Optional Filter to exclude specific expense records from the Batch being recreated based on ID.

Excluded Inventory Record ID’s

Optional Filter to exclude specific procurement records from the Batch being recreated based on ID.

Excluded Invoice Record ID’s

Optional Filter to exclude specific invoice records from the Batch being recreated based on ID.

Included Expense Record ID’s

Optional Filter to include specific expense records in the Batch being recreated based on ID.

Included Inventory Record ID’s

Optional Filter to include inventory records in the Batch being recreated based on ID.

Included Invoice Record ID’s

Optional Filter to include invoice records in the Batch being recreated based on ID.

Owner Level

Optional Filter to restrict the records that are returned in the batch being recreated based on Location (Level 2 of the Corporate Structure). You can specify the Location Description or Id.

Thru Date

Optional Filter to restrict the records that are returned in the batch being recreated based on the date they were taken. If no value is specified the default used by ConnectWise is the current date.

Zynk Settings

See Common Task Settings
